### 단건 주문 - 정상 (201 Created)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 단건 주문 - 회원 인증 헤더 누락 (401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 단건 주문 - 상품 미존재 (404 Not Found)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 99999, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 단건 주문 - 수량 0 (400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 0 }
  ]
}

### 단건 주문 - 재고 초과 (409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 999999 }
  ]
}

### 다중 항목 주문 - 정상 (201 Created)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 1 },
    { "productId": 2, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 다중 항목 주문 - 같은 상품 중복 (400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 1 },
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ]
}

### 다중 항목 주문 - 한 항목 재고 초과 (409 Conflict, 전체 원복)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 1 },
    { "productId": 2, "quantity": 999999 }
  ]
}

### 본인 주문 내역 - 기본 범위 (200 OK)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders?page=0&size=20
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

### 본인 주문 내역 - 날짜 범위 지정 (200 OK)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders?startAt=2026-01-01&endAt=2026-05-27&page=0&size=20
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

### 본인 주문 내역 - 시작일이 종료일보다 늦음 (400 Bad Request)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders?startAt=2026-02-10&endAt=2026-01-01&page=0&size=20
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

### 본인 주문 내역 - 회원 인증 헤더 누락 (401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders?page=0&size=20

### 본인 주문 상세 - 정상 (200 OK)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/1
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

### 본인 주문 상세 - 미존재 (404 Not Found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/99999
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

### 본인 주문 상세 - 회원 인증 헤더 누락 (401 Unauthorized)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/1

### 쿠폰 적용 주문 - 정상 (201 Created, 세 금액 + userCouponId)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "userCouponId": 1
}

### 쿠폰 적용 주문 - 쿠폰 미존재/타인 소유 (404 Not Found)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "userCouponId": 99999
}

### 쿠폰 적용 주문 - 사용됨/만료/최소금액 미달 (409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "userCouponId": 1
}
